title: Creative Team Jeph Loeb and Tim Sale Complete
description:
This is the complete works of Jeph Loeb and Tim Sale as a creative team. Arguably the best creative team in comics. 

This torrent includes:

     Batman: Haunted Knight
     Batman: The Long Halloween
     Batman: Dark Victory
     Catwoman: When in Rome
     Challengers of the Unknown Vol.2
     Daredevil: Yellow
     Hulk: Gray
     Spiderman: Blue
     Superman: For all Seasons
     Wolverine & Gambit: Victims

I also included Captain America: White #0
This is my first of what I hope are many compilation torrents and I must say Thanks to all the original scanners for their hard work. 
Thank god for DCP and The Minutemen!!
